A stone-and-bronze temple complex near @@WMafdet's@@N central market. Bronze claw sigils are set into the floor at the threshold, and the dim interior is lit by oil lamps that cast long shadows across the judgment benches. A petitioner's desk near the entrance handles enrollment for those who would serve the Shrine's oath-enforcement mission.

